name: Whoosh Nacchan
description:
Fly with Nacchan and Siichan through the Pear Sky Labyrinth!!!

　Fly to Siichan in the solo game.

　Fly with Nacchan and Siichan cooperating in the pair cooperation game.

　Fly with Nacchan and Siichan competing in the pair VS game.

　Nacchan:'Whoooosh!!! Sii---cha---n!!! I've come!!!'
　Siichan:'Naccha---n!!! Voooom---!!! Let's play!!!'

　Farewell, Nacchan!!!
　The final episode of Nacchan Trilogy!!!
